Controller

    • getFilter

      public void getFilter​(ViewPage2 vp2, javafx.scene.control.ComboBox<java.lang.String> cbox, java.util.ArrayList<Plant> plst, java.lang.String area, Garden g, javafx.scene.control.TabPane tp, javafx.scene.layout.HBox drop, javafx.scene.control.Tab t, javafx.scene.layout.VBox vb)
      Description: The filter method that organizes which combobox and which filter is applied. It filters the all plants (arraylist) given.
      Parameters:
      vp2 - : ViewPage2 object since the method needs the objects in vp2
      cbox - : the specified combobox (viewpage2 has 6 comboboxes)
      plst - : the plant arraylist: all plants from the Garden class
      area - : the type of combobox, in the Garden class the Filter() helps sort through which types
      g - : garden specified in ViewPage2
      tp - : tabPane specified in ViewPage2
      drop - : the hbox assembling the plant buttons and comboboxes
      t - : the main tab featuring the Plant Nursery with all buttons
      vb - : the vbox assembling the comboxes on the main tab

    • updateNursery

      public void updateNursery​(ViewPage2 vp2, java.util.ArrayList<Plant> plst, Garden g, javafx.scene.control.TabPane tp, javafx.scene.layout.HBox drop, javafx.scene.control.Tab t, javafx.scene.layout.VBox vb, java.lang.Boolean reset)
      Description: Updates the visual Plant Nursery display with the given paramters in ViewPage2. The parameters are needed to ensure no copies are created (only ViewPage2 objects). It displays the filtered or all plant buttons.
      Parameters:
      vp2 - ViewPage2 object to access methods and objects
      plst - a plant arraylist with applied filters
      g - a garden of viewpage2
      tp - a tabPane used in viewpage2
      drop - a dropdown used in viewpage2
      t - the main tab used in viewpage2
      vb - the dropdown format of comboboxes in viewpage2
      reset - a boolean to know whether to default to all 60 plants
